<body>

    <!-- Include navbar -->
    <%- include("includes/navbar.ejs") %>

        <div class="shipping-container">
            <div class="shipping-content-container">
                <h3>Return & Refund Policy</h3>
                <p>
                    Thank you for shopping with us at kharidlow.com! We are committed to ensuring a seamless shopping
                    experience. Please read the following policy carefully to understand our terms for cancellations,
                    returns, refunds, and COD orders.
                </p>

                <h4>1. TERMS OF CANCELLATION</h4>
                <ul style="list-style-type:lower-latin;">
                    <li><b>Cancellation Before Dispatch:</b>
                        <ul style="list-style-type:disc;">
                            <li>You can cancel your order anytime before it is dispatched by us.</li>
                            <li>Once the order is dispatched, cancellations will not be accepted.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><b>How to Cancel:</b>
                        <ul style="list-style-type:disc;">
                            <li>To cancel your order, contact us via WhatsApp at <span class="highlight">79825
                                    25575</span> with your order ID.</li>
                            <li>Refunds for cancellations will be processed within <span class="highlight">3 business
                                    days</span> of confirmation.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <h4>2. TERMS OF RETURN AND REFUND</h4>
                <p><b>(PARCEL OPENING VIDEO IS COMPULSORY.<br>
                        Without a proper parcel opening video, no claims will be entertained.)</b>
                </p>
                <ul style="list-style-type:lower-latin;">
                    <li><b>Eligible Returns:</b>
                        <p>We accept returns only in the following cases:</p>
                        <ul style="list-style-type:disc;">
                            <li><b>Manufacturing Defects:</b> If the product has a clear manufacturing defect.</li>
                            <li><b>Wrong Item Delivered:</b> If you receive an item that is different from what you
                                ordered.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><b>Return Process:</b>
                        <ul style="list-style-type:disc;">
                            <li>Report the issue within <span class="highlight">24 hours of delivery</span> by sending a
                                parcel opening video and the
                                package label to <span class="highlight">79825 25575</span>.</li>
                            <li>Upon validation of your claim, we will guide you on how to return the product.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><b>Return Shipping Charges:</b>
                        <ul style="list-style-type:disc;">
                            <li>Return shipping charges for eligible returns will be <span class="highlight">borne by
                                    us</span>.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><b>Refund Processing:</b>
                        <ul style="list-style-type:disc;">
                            <li>Refunds for eligible returns will be processed within <span class="highlight">24
                                    hours</span> of receiving and inspecting the returned product.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <p><b>Return Address:</b>
                    <br>
                    Nitvi Fashion Pvt Ltd: 25/89 Ground Floor Street Number 14 Vishwas Nagar, Shahdara Delhi-110032
                </p>

                <h4>3. NON-ELIGIBLE RETURNS</h4>
                <p>We do not accept returns in the following cases:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Change of mind or dislike of the product.</li>
                    <li>Damage caused due to improper handling by the customer.</li>
                    <li>Missing parcel opening video evidence.</li>
                </ul>

                <h4 style="font-weight: 700;">Need Help?</h4>
                <p>
                    For any questions related to shipping, you can reach us at
                <ul>
                    <li>Email: <span class="highlight">support@kharidlow.com</span></li>
                    <li>Phone/WhatsApp: <span class="highlight">+91 7982525575 / 8700711482</span></li>
                </ul>
                We’re here to assist you Monday through Saturday, 9 AM to 7 PM.
                <br><br>
                We’re dedicated to ensuring your orders reach you on time and in perfect condition. Thank you for
                choosing <span class="highlight">kharidlow.com</span>
                </p>
            </div>
